BB%84%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%9D%E5%AE%9D%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E5%8F%B6%E9%BB%84%E7%B4%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%B6%E7%B2%89%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E8%BE%85%E9%A3%9F%E3%80%82"><span class="nav-number">5.</span> <span class="nav-text">但叶黄素在母乳中的含量严重不足，而且人体自身也完全无法合成叶黄素，因此，应该为宝宝选择添加叶黄素的奶粉或者辅食。</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%8A%B1%E9%9D%92%E7%B4%A0"><span class="nav-number">6.</span> <span class="nav-text">花青素</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%99%BE%E9%9D%92%E7%B4%A0"><span class="nav-number">7.</span> <span class="nav-text">虾青素</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%BB%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%A0%E7%B1%BB"><span class="nav-number">8.</span> <span class="nav-text">维生素类</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%BB%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%A0C"><span class="nav-number">9.</span> <span class="nav-text">维生素C</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%BB%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%A0A"><span class="nav-number">10.</span> <span class="nav-text">维生素A</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%BB%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%A0B"><span class="nav-number">11.</span> <span class="nav-text">维生素B</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%89%9B%E7%A3%BA%E9%85%B8"><span class="nav-number">12.</span> <span class="nav-text">牛磺酸</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E9%92%99"><span class="nav-number">13.</span> <span class="nav-text">钙</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E9%93%AC"><span class="nav-number">14.</span> <span class="nav-text">铬</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E9%94%8C"><span class="nav-number">15.</span> <span class="nav-text">锌</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%B8%B8%E5%90%83%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E6%8B%A5%E6%9C%89%E5%A5%BD%E8%A7%86%E5%8A%9B"><span class="nav-number">16.</span> <span class="nav-text">常吃什么食物拥有好视力</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%AF%8C%E5%90%AB%E7%BB%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%A0A%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9"><span class="nav-number">17.</span> <span class="nav-text">富含维生素A的食物</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E8%82%9D%E8%84%8F%E3%80%81%E9%B1%BC%E8%82%9D%E6%B2%B9%E3%80%81%E9%B1%BC%E5%8D%B5%E3%80%81%E7%A6%BD%E8%9B%8B%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%E9%99%A4%E6%AD%A4%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E8%83%A1%E8%90%9D%E5%8D%9C%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E8%8F%9C%E3%80%81%E5%8D%B7%E5%BF%83%E8%8F%9C%E3%80%81%E8%8B%8B%E8%8F%9C%E3%80%81%E8%8B%9C%E8%93%BF%E3%80%81%E7%BA%A2%E5%BF%83%E7%94%9C%E8%96%AF%E3%80%81%E5%8D%97%E7%93%9C%E3%80%81%E9%9D%92%E8%BE%A3%E6%A4%92%E7%AD%89%E8%94%AC%E8%8F%9C"><span class="nav-number">18.</span> <span class="nav-text">各种动物肝脏、鱼肝油、鱼卵、禽蛋等。除此之外，胡萝卜、生菜、卷心菜、苋菜、苜蓿、红心甜薯、南瓜、青辣椒等蔬菜</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%8F%A0%E8%8F%9C"><span class="nav-number">19.</span> <span class="nav-text">菠菜</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%AF%8C%E5%90%AB%E7%BB%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%A0C%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E6%9E%9C"><span class="nav-number">20.</span> <span class="nav-text">富含维生素C的水果</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%8C%95%E7%8C%B4%E6%A1%83%E3%80%81%E6%A9%99%E5%AD%90%E3%80%81%E6%9F%A0%E6%AA%AC%E3%80%81%E6%9E%B8%E6%9D%9E%E3%80%81%E5%B1%B1%E6%A5%82%E7%AD%89%E8%BF%99%E7%B1%BB%E5%AF%8C%E5%90%AB%E7%BB%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%A0C-%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%91%84%E5%85%A5%E9%87%8F%E3%80%82%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E6%9F%BF%E5%AD%90%E6%A4%92%E3%80%81%E8%A5%BF%E7%BA%A2%E6%9F%BF%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B0%E9%B2%9C%E8%94%AC%E8%8F%9C"><span class="nav-nu